{"tid":785321,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家有冇試過發成真夢?","createTime":"2018-08-19T06:23:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-19T11:08:46.000Z","uid":193015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"bebd4353fbf347adc8d2f86ca539e226602127c1","tid":785321,"uid":193015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T06:23:33.000Z","msg":"好記得試過一次<br />\n係起我幾歲既時候<br />\n<br />\n個夢係屋企<br />\n呀媽買完餸番黎<br />\n除左d餸之外<br />\n仲有一大包零食<br />\n之後加姐打開個袋睇入面有咩零食<br />\n之後之拎上枱面<br />\n而我加姐仲即時開左一包紫色既蝦條<br />\n食完仲講左句(好辣呀)<br />\n之後就醒左<br />\n<br />\n醒完之後行出廳<br />\n就發生番一模一樣既事<br />\n我都驚左一驚<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲都發過成真夢呢?"},{"pid":"60bb0556586765e8fc8bc78c0e1a1bd60d5aa3eb","tid":785321,"uid":157864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T10:49:35.000Z","msg":"我都係好耐以前試過一次<br />\n果陣小學一定二年班，發夢冒簽左屋企人個名<br />\n點知呀媽朝早執我書包果陣見到<br />\n之後俾佢鬧<br />\n<br />\n訓醒完，情景係一模一樣"},{"pid":"788db7e1b917292682a9fb415c63b12375910699","tid":785321,"uid":23486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T10:51:06.000Z","msg":"Deja vu?"},{"pid":"7a242573b7c854767be8ca6f9565ef8f5d3fde13","tid":785321,"uid":193378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T10:51:54.000Z","msg":"既視感"},{"pid":"46d0a9c9db1546afd113578c205f27c4bffb86c0","tid":785321,"uid":4596,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"788db7e1b917292682a9fb415c63b12375910699","tid":785321,"uid":23486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T10:51:06.000Z","msg":"Deja vu?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T10:52:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/dv13gl0a-FA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fdv13gl0a-FA&d=nQmoHIdi91iVTh58cZr5n8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=1acdd910\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/dv13gl0a-FA</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01f966da2e07136f6ec07ce243b7b8b496da367a","tid":785321,"uid":180035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T11:08:46.000Z","msg":"果時係台灣夢見有架機車比車撞 條友同車彈飛左<br />\n醒左肚餓落樓下食野 見到有警車係十字路口<br />\n旁邊有架機車係地下 封左路"}]}